<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="28">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="28">
One of the four known &quot;inland island&quot; species of 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Buthus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Buthus" order="Scorpiones" pageId="13" pageNumber="28" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Buthus</taxonomicName>
